{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2054633, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "公开之后相对之前不公开至少可以更公平的内卷", "timestamp": 1626110785, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054635, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "# 意义： 老子卷得那么辛苦，其他人也给我卷 🐶", "timestamp": 1626110793, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054637, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是囚徒困境", "timestamp": 1626110812, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054638, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054633, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 学习不用太卷  多卷其他方面", "timestamp": 1626110840, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054643, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054638, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那也比原来只卷学习要更好一点", "timestamp": 1626110876, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054643, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 或许吧  可是小镇做题家只会学习…", "timestamp": 1626111029, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054681, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054658, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 哎，总得走出舒适圈吧", "timestamp": 1626111314, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054685, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054681, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不走 我就要苟在舒适区", "timestamp": 1626111369, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054721, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在的情况是，少部分人掌握课程资料，采用应试的方式进行无意义内卷，其他人看到他们用这种方式尝到了甜头，也想要课程资料，内卷范围扩大\n而公开课程资料后，假设绝大部分同学都拿到了资料，就可以倒逼老师通过更改考核内容等方式对这种行为进行制裁，从而杜绝内卷", "timestamp": 1626111738, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054727, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054721, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 老师未必会改啊。。。", "timestamp": 1626111825, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054685, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 学校多次改革就是为了模糊化绩点，将小镇做题家赶出舒适区，却不曾想，越改革，绩点越重要，大家越是要卷绩点", "timestamp": 1626111886, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054735, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054727, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 确实，但比如如果老师知道很多人都有他往年的考题的话，应该也就会换题了吧？", "timestamp": 1626112009, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054745, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054735, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 但是就是没有往年题哇😭", "timestamp": 1626112147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2054748, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054735, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 有可能是把泄露题的人搞了，杀一儆百", "timestamp": 1626112170, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2055038, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": 2054735, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 有机A某个老师至少从13年开始就没换过题了……而且他肯定知道自己的题目广为流传", "timestamp": 1626132020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2055068, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 400856, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "反正我大一完知道很多人人都有资料并且资料里很多原题的时候懵了", "timestamp": 1626133297, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 400856, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "公开课程资料的意义在哪？\ndz在清华上了两年学，学习过程中几乎从来不参考往届的课程资料，期末考前可能做做往年题刷手感，因为过度依赖它以及其背后代表的考核就是把高等教育的一部分再度异化为应试教育（而这一点本来可能避免）\n公开课程资料只会加剧不以掌握知识为核心的无意义内卷……", "timestamp": 1626110703, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626136180, "url": "", "vote": {}}}